{"tid":1587254,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支那湖南貨車「煞車失靈」衝撞市集！路人遭捲車底「四肢濺血變形」釀10死16傷","createTime":"2019-09-22T10:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T13:55:16.000Z","uid":135488,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9894b910a159f5426abda33ca411bf97f057cc49","tid":1587254,"uid":135488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:27:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記者朱世凱／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n湖南省湘潭市有一輛貨車今（22）日突然撞向趕往市集的民眾，許多人當場被捲入車底甚至輾過，事故造成至少10死16傷。據悉，肇事駕駛已被警方拘捕，官方則稱，車禍原因與煞車失靈有關。<br />\n<br />\n綜合陸媒報導，事發在人來人往的一處市集，早上8點30左右突然衝進一輛大貨車。影像顯示，藍色貨車撞向市集後波及周遭攤販和民眾，現場相當混亂，雜物及商品都散滿一地，還有不少民眾四肢扭曲變形，受傷倒地，地面滿是不忍直視的血跡。<br />\n<br />\n報導提到，肇事司機是當地人，全部傷者都已送往醫院搶救中，事故導致至少10死16傷。肇事的貨車車牌為湘A20816。警方初步調查後指出，原因很可能和煞車失靈有關，加上早上市集民眾較多，才會造成現場狀況如此慘烈。當局則稱，已展開應急處置，不過具體傷亡還在統計中，後續會透過官方通道通報。</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190922/1540812.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190922%2F1540812.htm&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBibpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=8530dad5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190922/1540812.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ed45ca80444b3165a2053d639156e08ac167b5f2","tid":1587254,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:27:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cdc9a2b55ecf0093536d39e2da6c4e05933db5f3","tid":1587254,"uid":135488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:29:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e1281c35bf339aa0f04fd811e6ef91138978ed","tid":1587254,"uid":135488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a9ab8e2d65e3ace01068aeba6b0b1af1b4a245","tid":1587254,"uid":135488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934f354f98fc017b8a2fdd148606eb863d6c7711","tid":1587254,"uid":299537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:55:16.000Z","msg":"1. 湘潭係毛主席嘅鄉下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 8點30分左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}